    /// The x87 FPU is a 16-bits register whose fields are as follows:
    ///
    /// | 12-15 | 10-11 | 8-9 | 6-7 |  5 |  4 |  3 |  2 |  1 |  0 |
    /// |------:|------:|----:|----:|---:|---:|---:|---:|---:|---:|
    /// |       | RC    | PC  |     | PM | UM | OM | ZM | DM | IM |
